2402	  \uses{lem:mathlib_spec_fullyFaithful, lem:mathlib_isOpenImmersion_mono,
2403	        lem:mathlib_isAffineOpen_isoSpec, lem:mathlib_commRingCat_epi_iff_epi,
2404	        lem:mathlib_algebra_isEpi}
2405	  Let \(U \le V\) be affine opens of a scheme \(S\). Then the structure-sheaf restriction
2406	  \(\Gamma(S, V) \to \Gamma(S, U)\) is a ring epimorphism, i.e.\
2407	  \(\mathrm{Algebra.IsEpi}\,\Gamma(S, V)\,\Gamma(S, U)\).
